I have to find this funny that I logged on here and if it was a book it would be very dusty because its been a year and when reading my last post I realised something a year on and I am still saying that I am going to focus on my weight and go have a one week detox plan that week has yet to come.

I am fed up with blogs I cant keep up with them I have a bout 10000 or well thats just what it feels like.
I can not say like last time that I will keep up with this one as I as you probably know already am not true to my word.

Tommorow I go to party in the park in Leeds - Temple Newsm with Mel.M gunna be fun I just hope Mel likes at least one of the people who go I personally am looking forward to the headliner M.J Blidge.

In the last year not much has changed I have become an Ipoder hopefully I wont have a future like the Simpsons predicted with mine.
I am sill your acting,day-dreamer who likes taking photographs with her new camera and thinking of cool ways to right a book.
The last thing like many others I have been planning for many years now.

Prefesions are beginging to get to me I think that is because I am loosing the point I just dont get it anymore I was at the opening of Harry Potter and the order of the phonix then I read the next book The half-blooded prince in 1 and a half days and now I am here anxusly awaiting the next and final Harry potter book planning how I am going to make a fan music video from Harry Potter & also thinking (if that aint enough) weather I should right my own book but then reality sure enough checks in and I begin to see the point my mind has been making out to me who would want to  read the shit that you personally put in front of them and that is just one of the reasons I am not on a word document now.

Personally Signed 
Cora
